OL,6,CG1946FJohn Logie Baird dies. He was
OL,7,Fone of the inventors of mechanical
OL,8,Ftelevision and demonstrated the first
OL,9,Fworking television system on 26th
OL,10,FJanuary 1926. He was the inventor of
OL,11,Fboth the first publicly demonstrated
OL,12,Fcolour television system and the first
OL,13,Fpurely electronic colour television
OL,14,Fpicture tube.
